rounded-xl text-xs font-bold border border-slate-200 shadow-sm\">Smart Slides</span><span class=\"px-4 py-2 bg-white text-slate-600 rounded-xl text-xs font-bold border border-slate-200 shadow-sm\">Past Questions</span></div></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-12 md:gap-24\"><div class=\"flex-1 w-full\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden aspect-[4/3] rounded-[3rem] shadow-2xl shadow-slate-200\"><div style=\"height:120%;top:-10%;position:relative;transform:translateY(-40px)\"><img alt=\"Student working\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fstudents%2Fearn.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fstudents%2Fearn.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fstudents%2Fearn.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fstudents%2Fearn.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fstudents%2Fearn.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fstudents%2Fearn.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fstudents%2Fearn.png&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fstudents%2Fearn.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fstudents%2Fearn.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-slate-900/40 to-transparent pointer-events-none\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-6 left-8 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-md px-4 py-2 rounded-xl text-primary font-black text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest shadow-lg z-10\">Phase 2: Economic Power</div></div></div><div class=\"flex-1 text-center md:text-left\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:none\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-6 leading-tight\">Earn <br/><span class=\"text-primary-light\">Your Way.</span></h2><p class=\"text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8\">Find campus gigs, sell textbooks, and trade gadgets in our marketplace. Plus, earn Looms for your academic contributions.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-center md:justify-start gap-3\"><span class=\"px-4 py-2 bg-white text-slate-600 rounded-xl text-xs font-bold border border-slate-200 shadow-sm\">Campus Gigs</span><span class=\"px-4 py-2 bg-white text-slate-600 rounded-xl text-xs font-bold border border-slate-200 shadow-sm\">Marketplace</span><span class=\"px-4 py-2 bg-white text-slate-600 rounded-xl text-xs font-bold border border-slate-200 shadow-sm\">Looms Rewards</span></div></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12 md:gap-24\"><div class=\"flex-1 w-full\"><div class=\"relative overflow-hidden aspect-[4/3] rounded-[3rem] shadow-2xl shadow-slate-200\"><div style=\"height:120%;top:-10%;position:relative;transform:translateY(-40px)\"><img alt=\"Campus life\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fstudents%2Fconnect.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fstudents%2Fconnect.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fstudents%2Fconnect.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fstudents%2Fconnect.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fstudents%2Fconnect.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fstudents%2Fconnect.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fstudents%2Fconnect.png&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fstudents%2Fconnect.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fstudents%2Fconnect.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-slate-900/40 to-transparent pointer-events-none\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-6 left-8 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-md px-4 py-2 rounded-xl text-primary font-black text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest shadow-lg z-10\">Phase 3: Deep Connection</div></div></div><div class=\"flex-1 text-center md:text-left\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:none\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-6 leading-tight\">Connect <br/><span class=\"text-primary\">Beyond Borders.</span></h2><p class=\"text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8\">Stay updated with campus news, join anonymous discussions, and see what&#x27;s trending across all universities in Ghana.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-center md:justify-start gap-3\"><span class=\"px-4 py-2 bg-white text-slate-600 rounded-xl text-xs font-bold border border-slate-200 shadow-sm\">Social Feed</span><span class=\"px-4 py-2 bg-white text-slate-600 rounded-xl text-xs font-bold border border-slate-200 shadow-sm\">Campus News</span><span class=\"px-4 py-2 bg-white text-slate-600 rounded-xl text-xs font-bold border border-slate-200 shadow-sm\">UniClips</span></div></div></div></section><section id=\"features\" class=\"w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto py-32 border-t border-slate-200 relative px-6\"><div class=\"text-center mb-20\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:none\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-4\">The Complete Ecosystem.</h2><p class=\"text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-[0.4em] font-bold text-xs leading-loose\">Everything you need to own your university journey</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:none\"><div class=\"group glass-light p-8 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-100 hover:border-primary-light/30 transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-primary/5 cursor-default relative overflow-hidden h-full\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-24 h-24 bg-primary/5 blur-[40px] rounded-full group-hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors\"></div><div class=\"relative mb-6\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform text-primary-light shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-book-open w-6 h-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 7v14\"></path><path d=\"M3 18a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h5a4 4 0 0 1 4 4 4 4 0 0 1 4-4h5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v13a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-6a3 3 0 0 0-3 3 3 3 0 0 0-3-3z\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"mb-4\"><span class=\"text-[9px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 px-3 py-1 rounded-full\">Learn</span></div><h3 class=\"relative text-xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">Smart Learning Hub</h3><p class=\"relative text-slate-500 font-medium text-sm leading-relaxed\">Access AI-powered study tools, flashcards, practice tests, and past questions to ace your courses.</p></div><div class=\"group glass-light p-8 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-100 hover:border-primary-light/30 transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-primary/5 cursor-default relative overflow-hidden h-full\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-24 h-24 bg-primary/5 blur-[40px] rounded-full group-hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors\"></div><div class=\"relative mb-6\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform text-primary shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sparkles w-6 h-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11.017 2.814a1 1 0 0 1 1.966 0l1.051 5.558a2 2 0 0 0 1.594 1.594l5.558 1.051a1 1 0 0 1 0 1.966l-5.558 1.051a2 2 0 0 0-1.594 1.594l-1.051 5.558a1 1 0 0 1-1.966 0l-1.051-5.558a2 2 0 0 0-1.594-1.594l-5.558-1.051a1 1 0 0 1 0-1.966l5.558-1.051a2 2 0 0 0 1.594-1.594z\"></path><path d=\"M20 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M22 4h-4\"></path><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"20\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg></div></div><div class=\"mb-4\"><span class=\"text-[9px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 px-3 py-1 rounded-full\">Earn</span></div><h3 class=\"relative text-xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">Looms &amp; Rewards</h3><p class=\"relative text-slate-500 font-medium text-sm leading-relaxed\">Earn Looms for your academic contributions and community engagement. Real value for real student effort.</p></div><div class=\"group glass-light p-8 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-100 hover:border-primary-light/30 transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-primary/5 cursor-default relative overflow-hidden h-full\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-24 h-24 bg-primary/5 blur-[40px] rounded-full group-hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors\"></div><div class=\"relative mb-6\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform text-primary-light shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shopping-bag w-6 h-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 10a4 4 0 0 1-8 0\"></path><path d=\"M3.103 6.034h17.794\"></path><path d=\"M3.4 5.467a2 2 0 0 0-.4 1.2V20a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V6.667a2 2 0 0 0-.4-1.2l-2-2.667A2 2 0 0 0 17 2H7a2 2 0 0 0-1.6.8z\"></pa