7 6.998a2 2 0 0 1 .003 3.458l-12 7A2 2 0 0 1 5 19z\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"mb-4\"><span class=\"text-[9px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 px-3 py-1 rounded-full\">Connect</span></div><h3 class=\"relative text-xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">UniClips</h3><p class=\"relative text-slate-500 font-medium text-sm leading-relaxed\">Short-form video content created by and for university students. Learn, laugh, and share definir moments.</p></div><div class=\"group glass-light p-8 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-100 hover:border-primary-light/30 transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-primary/5 cursor-default relative overflow-hidden h-full\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-24 h-24 bg-primary/5 blur-[40px] rounded-full group-hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors\"></div><div class=\"relative mb-6\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform text-primary shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-newspaper w-6 h-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 18h-5\"></path><path d=\"M18 14h-8\"></path><path d=\"M4 22h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V4a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H8a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 1-4 0v-9a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2\"></path><rect width=\"8\" height=\"4\" x=\"10\" y=\"6\" rx=\"1\"></rect></svg></div></div><div class=\"mb-4\"><span class=\"text-[9px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 px-3 py-1 rounded-full\">Connect</span></div><h3 class=\"relative text-xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">Campus News &amp; Events</h3><p class=\"relative text-slate-500 font-medium text-sm leading-relaxed\">Stay up to date with campus news, upcoming events, concerts, and activities from your university and beyond.</p></div><div class=\"group glass-light p-8 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-100 hover:border-primary-light/30 transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-primary/5 cursor-default relative overflow-hidden h-full\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-24 h-24 bg-primary/5 blur-[40px] rounded-full group-hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors\"></div><div class=\"relative mb-6\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform text-primary-light shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-user-check w-6 h-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m16 11 2 2 4-4\"></path><path d=\"M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2\"></path><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\"></circle></svg></div></div><div class=\"mb-4\"><span class=\"text-[9px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 px-3 py-1 rounded-full\">All</span></div><h3 class=\"relative text-xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">Verified Community</h3><p class=\"relative text-slate-500 font-medium text-sm leading-relaxed\">A safe, university-verified environment exclusively for students. Your campus identity, protected.</p></div></div></section><section id=\"how\" class=\"w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto py-32 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-20 px-6\"><div class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:none\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-10 leading-tight\">Getting Started <br/>is <span class=\"text-primary-light italic\">Actually</span> Easy.</h2></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-12\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:none\"><div class=\"flex gap-6 group\"><span class=\"text-4xl font-black text-slate-200 group-hover:text-primary-light/40 transition-colors\">01</span><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-1\"><h4 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-slate-900\">Download the App</h4><p class=\"text-slate-600 font-medium\">Get Uniloomy free from the App Store or Google Play.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:none\"><div class=\"flex gap-6 group\"><span class=\"text-4xl font-black text-slate-200 group-hover:text-primary-light/40 transition-colors\">02</span><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-1\"><h4 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-slate-900\">Verify Your Campus</h4><p class=\"text-slate-600 font-medium\">Provide your university, program details, and student ID card for quick, secure verification.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:none\"><div class=\"flex gap-6 group\"><span class=\"text-4xl font-black text-slate-200 group-hover:text-primary-light/40 transition-colors\">03</span><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-1\"><h4 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-slate-900\">Start Your Journey</h4><p class=\"text-slate-600 font-medium\">Explore study tools, see trending UniClips, join anonymous chats, and stay updated with campus news from day one.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"flex-1 w-full\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:none\"><div class=\"bg-slate-50 rounded-[3rem] aspect-square flex items-center justify-center border border-slate-200 shadow-sm relative overflow-hidden group\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-primary/5 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"></div><div class=\"text-center p-12 relative\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" strok